s a small news section, mostly for schedule changes.</p><p>The customer already had a server administrator, so I was not required to maintain this website.</p></div></div></article></div></div><div class="project"><div class="blurred-container"><article><div class="meta-container"><figure class="loading"><div class="loader"><div></div><div></div></div><img data-src="img/projects/hiades-cover.jpg" alt="Hiades"></figure><div class="file"><div><span>Year</span><p>2015</p></div><div><span>Status</span><p>Ended</p></div><div><span>Company</span><p>Hiades</p></div><div><span>Based</span><p>Córdoba, Argentina</p></div></div></div><div class="info"><div class="title"><h5>Position - Web Developer</h5><h2>Hiades</h2></div><div class="content"><p>I was the only developer on this agency, this was my last position as an employee.</p><p>It was my first time working on a interdisciplinary environment, working with marketers and community managers.</p><p>I made multiple projects here, with different reqirements, such as real state, food services, architecture websites.</p></div></div></article></div></div><div class="project"><div class="blurred-container"><article><div class="meta-container"><figure class="loading"><div class="loader"><div></div><div></div></div><img data-src="img/projects/alus-cover.jpg" alt="Alus"></figure><div class="file"><div><span>Year</span><p>2014</p></div><div><span>Status</span><p>Ended</p></div><div><span>Company</span><p>Alus Creativos</p></div><div><span>Based</span><p>Córdoba, Argentina</p></div></div></div><div class="info"><div class="title"><h5>Position - Web Developer</h5><h2>Alus Creativos</h2></div><div class="content"><p>This was my first experience working as a web developer/designer.</p><p>I made few website projects for multiple customers with HTML, CSS, JS and Wordpress.</p></div></div></article></div></div></div><div id="stim-demo" class="project-demo"><button class="btn-main leave-demo" data-target="stim-demo"><svg aria-hidden="true" foc